  "title": "Xtra Creamy Egyptian Mung Bean Sprouts Curry",
  "description": "A kid-friendly Egyptian dish featuring mung bean sprouts in a creamy and mildly spicy curry sauce, flavored with a hint of mustard and ayurvedic-sattvic friendly ingredients.",
